claim.claim-text:
A lawn mower apparatus comprising:
a body (4) including a driver;
a rotatable plate (2) connected to the driver and rotatably mounted on one face of the body (4);
a blade (3) rotatably connected to an edge of the rotatable plate (2); and
a blade protection cover (1) removably coupled to the blade (3),
wherein the blade protection cover (1) includes:
a first cover (100) for covering one face of the blade (3);
two second covers (200) connected to the first cover (100), both second covers (200) covering both edges of the blade (3) in a width direction of the blade (3), respectively; and
a guide (201) disposed on inner faces of the second covers (200), respectively, wherein the guides (201) are constructed to guide the blade protection cover (1) to slide along both edges in the width direction of the blade (3) and thus to be coupled to the blade (3).
